# CLAUDE.md

This file configures Claude Code for your vault.

## Folder Structure

```
daily/              # Daily notes
daily/today.md      # Current day (always here)
daily/archive/      # Previous days (YYYY/MM-month/)
daily/templates/    # Note templates
projects/           # Project notes (optional)
```

## Daily Note

- Today's note is always: `daily/today.md`
- Archive location: `daily/archive/YYYY/MM-month/YYYY-MM-DD.md`
- Template: `daily/templates/daily-template.md`

## Morning Routine

Run `/start-my-day` to:
1. Archive yesterday's note
2. Create fresh today.md
3. Process brain dump section
4. Suggest priorities

## Quick Commands

| Say | Claude Does |
|-----|-------------|
| `/start-my-day` | Full morning routine |
| "process my brain dump" | Extract tasks from Brain Dump section |
| "what should I focus on?" | Suggest priorities based on today.md |
| "carry forward" | Move incomplete tasks to today |

---

*Customize this file to match your vault structure.*
